  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824500/extras/1ea7a6e66f728e5cb0cd777ebe0109fe.poster.avif?t=1753218957\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824500/extras/1ea7a6e66f728e5cb0cd777ebe0109fe.webm?t=1753218957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824500/extras/1ea7a6e66f728e5cb0cd777ebe0109fe.mp4?t=1753218957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Shockwaves is a puzzle game inspired by the popular 2048. In Shockwaves, placing numbers triggers powerful shockwaves that push other numbers across the board. When similar numbers collide, they merge, setting off a chain reaction of shockwaves and creating exciting combo effects that boost your score.<br><br><strong>FEATURES:</strong><br><strong>ENDLESS MODE:</strong> Compete against friends and players worldwide on the leaderboard in an endless mode.<br><br><strong>PUZZLES:</strong> Challenge yourself with 50 puzzles that progressively get harder.<br><br><strong>CHALLENGES:</strong> Put your skills to the test with 16 open-ended challenges that encourage creative thinking and strategic gameplay.<br><br><strong>LEADERBOARDS:</strong> Showcase your skills on integrated leaderboards.",
